\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\varepsilon=\frac{0.2}{r_{c}}\implies S_{01}=w_{1}\frac{0.2}{r_{c}}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

where 
\begin_inset Formula $\varepsilon$
\end_inset

